### Feedback — operator decision on an agent suggestion
###
### Submitting feedback both inserts a Feedback row AND mutates the parent
### order's status based on finalAction. Listen on /ws/orders to see the
### order.status_changed event delivered live.

@host = http://localhost:8000

# @name login
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=admin&password=admin123


# ============================================================================
# POST /api/feedback
# ============================================================================
### Pick an orderId that has a suggestion (agent action populated in
### `GET /api/orders?status=pending_review`).

### Decision: ACCEPTED — agent was right, approve the order
POST {{host}}/api/feedback
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "67e766c7-b1cf-4628-a3d0-ebf911330522",
  "operatorDecision": "accepted",
  "finalAction": "approve",
  "operatorReason": "Looks normal, matches recent history."
}

###

### Decision: MODIFIED — agent suggested approve, operator escalates instead
POST {{host}}/api/feedback
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "67e766c7-b1cf-4628-a3d0-ebf911330522",
  "operatorDecision": "modified",
  "finalAction": "escalate",
  "operatorReason": "Quantity outlier — escalating despite agent confidence."
}

###

### Decision: REJECTED — agent was wrong, request clarification from supplier
POST {{host}}/api/feedback
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "operatorDecision": "rejected",
  "finalAction": "request_clarification",
  "operatorReason": "Agent missed the typo in productCode; ask supplier."
}

###

### Unknown order → 404
POST {{host}}/api/feedback
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "operatorDecision": "accepted",
  "finalAction": "approve"
}
